Dangote Group of Companies has disclosed that the Dangote Fertiliser will operate a special help desk for customers and farmers during the ongoing Kaduna International Trade Fair. A statement from the Corporate Communication Department of the Dangote Group said apart from the products which are sold at reasonable prices with special packages, gift items are also being presented to customers at the pavilion. Encouraged by the huge investments and philanthropic activities of the Dangote Group of companies, President Muhammadu Buhari and his host, the governor of Kaduna State, hailed the president of the Dangote Group, Alhaji Aliko Dangote. President Buhari, who was represented by the Minister of Industry, Trade and Investment, Otunba Niyi Adebayo, made the commendation when he visited the Dangote pavilion at the ongoing 43rd Kaduna International Trade Fair where he said the country is grateful for the humongous support the Dangote Group is offering the nation.